{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01EGJDFTr2WFqqsb1zBHztGP","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All 36 tests pass. \n\n**Changes made to `lib/text-classifier/title-extractor.ts`:**\n\n1. **`startsWithNumber`** (line 101): Extended regex to include Unicode fraction characters (`½⅓⅔¼¾⅕⅖⅗⅘⅙⅚⅛⅜⅝⅞`), so lines like `½ red onion` are correctly identified as ingredients.\n\n2. **`isBodyProse`** (new helper before `isTitleAbsentPage`): Returns `true` for lines starting with a lowercase letter with 4+ words — reliable signal for mid-recipe prose continuation since titles are always capitalized.\n\n3. **`isTitleAbsentPage`**: Now includes `isBodyProse(line)` in the `.every()` check, so pages starting with prose like `reduce heat and stir...` are correctly identified as mid-recipe pages.\n\nThe iteration 23 last-resort fallback is unaffected: the `titleAbsent` guard at line 1235 already allows position-0 candidates with `rawScore >= 0.10` to survive into `selected`, so they never reach the last-resort path."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":288,"cache_read_input_tokens":33396,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":288},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"149152b5-5016-41c0-93eb-7191e3713674","uuid":"4c3a08e9-cc78-40d6-a1c5-57c4095d616c"}
